   ### File & Directory Permissions ###

## Create devops_workspace directory and a file project_notes.txt.
   mkdir devops_workspace
   touch project_notes.txt
## set permission for both owner can edit, group can read, others have no access.
   chmod 640 devops_workspace
   chmod 640 project_notes.txt
## change ownership of project_notes.txt file to another user
   sudo chown user2 project_notes.txt                            ## where user2 is an another user 
